findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions includeInReward(), _getCurrentSupply(), and bulkAntiBot() use loops which can cause an OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long excluded addresses list.

findings.title: Potential unlimited minting of sundae tokens
findings.description: The contract owner has the ability to update the amount of tokens needed to trigger swapping and liquidity, which can potentially lead to unlimited minting of Sundae tokens.
